\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{P}_{1}\left(\left\{ x_{0}\right\} \right)=\mathcal{P}_{2}\left(\left\{ x_{0}\right\} \right)=0$
\end_inset

 עם זאת 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{P}_{1}\neq\mathcal{P}_{2}$
\end_inset


