\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{P}\left(A_{1}\cup A_{2}\right)=\mathcal{P}\left(A_{1}\right)+\mathcal{P}\left(A_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

.
 אם 
\begin_inset Formula $A\subseteq B$
\end_inset

 אז 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{P}\left(A\right)\leq\mathcal{P}\left(B\right)$
\end_inset

 אז 
\begin_inset Formula $B=A\cup\left(B\setminus A\right)$
\end_inset

 איחוד זר.
